#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:210
msgid "*waptwua* packages"
msgstr "Les paquets *waptwua*"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:212
msgid ""
"*waptwua* packages contain the list of authorized or prohibited Windows "
"Updates."
msgstr ""
"Les paquets *waptwua* contiennent le liste des mises à jour Windows "
"autorisées et interdites."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:214
msgid ""
"When this package is installed on the endpoint, the next update scan "
"performed by WAPT will choose Windows updates based on this filtering."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque ce paquet est installé sur le terminal, la prochaine analyse de "
"mise à jour effectuée par WAPT choisira les mises à jour Windows en "
"fonction de ce filtrage."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:217
msgid ""
"If the host has several *waptwua* packages, then WAPT will merge all "
"package rules."
msgstr ""
"Si la machine a plusieurs listes de paquets *waptwua* applicables, alors "
"WAPT combine les règles."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:220
msgid ""
"When this package is installed on the host, the next :command:`update` "
"will scan for official Windows updates applicable to the host based on "
"this filtering."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque ce paquet est installé sur l'hôte, le prochain :command:`update` "
"recherchera les mises à jour officielles de Windows applicables à l'hôte "
"en fonction de ce filtrage."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:224
msgid "*selfservice* packages"
msgstr "Les paquets *self-service*"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:228
msgid ""
"*selfservice* packages contain a list of groups or users (Active "
"Directory or local) and their associated lists of authorized packages "
"that Users are allowed to install by themselves."
msgstr ""
"Les paquets *self-service* contiennent une liste de groupes ou "
"d'utilisateurs (Active Directory ou local) et leurs listes associées de "
"paquets que les utilisateurs seront autorisés à installer par eux-mêmes."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:233
msgid "*profile* packages"
msgstr "Les paquets *profile*"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:237
msgid "*profile* packages are similar to *group* packages."
msgstr "Les paquets *profile* sont similaires aux paquets *groupe*."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:239
msgid ""
"However, *profile* packages work a little differently and are most useful"
" when an Active Directory Server is operating within the "
":term:`Organization`:"
msgstr ""
"Cependant, les paquets *profile* fonctionnent un peu différemment et sont"
" plus utiles lorsqu'un serveur Active Directory fonctionne dans "
"l':term:`Organisation` :"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:242
msgid ""
"the WAPT agent will list the Active Directory groups where the host "
"belongs;"
msgstr ""
"l'agent WAPT listera les groupes Active Directory auxquels appartient "
"l'hôte ;"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:244
msgid ""
"if a *profile* package has the same name as the Active Directory group, "
"then the WAPT agent will install automatically the *profile* package for "
"the Active Directory group of which it is a member;"
msgstr ""
"si un paquet *profile* porte le même nom que le groupe Active Directory, "
"l'agent WAPT installera automatiquement le paquet *profile* pour le "
"groupe Active Directory auquel il appartient ;"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:248
msgid ""
"If the host is no longer a member of its Active Directory group, then the"
" *profile* package will be uninstalled."
msgstr ""
"Si l'hôte n'est plus membre de son groupe Active Directory, le paquet "
"*profile* sera désinstallé."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:253
msgid ""
"For performance reasons, this feature is enabled only if the "
"*use_ad_groups* option is enabled in :file:`wapt-get.ini`."
msgstr ""
"Pour des raisons de performance, cette fonctionnalité n'est activée que "
"si l'option *use_ad_groups* est activée dans :file:`wapt-get.ini`."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:257
msgid "Dependency mechanism"
msgstr "Principe de dépendances"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:259
msgid "In WAPT everything works on the principle of dependencies."
msgstr "Dans WAPT tout fonctionne selon le principe des dépendances."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:261
msgid ""
"By default, the WAPT agent will look for its host package. The *host* "
"package lists packages to install on the computer."
msgstr ""
"Par défaut, le client WAPT va chercher à installer son paquet machine. Le"
" paquet *host* listera les autres paquets à installer sur la machine."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:264
msgid ""
"The *host* package is correctly installed when all its dependencies are "
"satisfied."
msgstr ""
"Ainsi, le paquet *host* sera correctement installé si toutes ses "
"dépendances sont satisfaites."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:267
msgid ""
"Each sub-dependency must be satisfied to satisfy an upper-level "
"dependency."
msgstr "Chaque dépendance devra satisfaire aux sous-dépendances et ainsi de suite."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:269
msgid ""
"When every dependency is satisfied, the host notifies its status to the "
"WAPT Server and its indicator turns **OK** and green in the WAPT console,"
" meaning the host has the host profile that the :term:`Administrator` or "
":term:`Package Deployer` has defined for it."
msgstr ""
"Quand toutes les dépendances sont satisfaites, la machine remonte en état"
" **OK** dans la console, signifiant que la machine est conforme au profil"
" que l':term:`Administrateur` ou le :term:`Déployeur de Paquets` aura "
"défini pour elle."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:278
msgid "Conceptual diagram of the dependency mechanism"
msgstr "Schéma conceptuel de la notion de dépendance"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:282
msgid ""
"When attributing a software package to a host as a dependency, only the "
"software canonical name without its version number is registered as a "
"dependency (ex: I want Freemind to be installed on this machine in its "
"latest version and :program:`Freemind` to be configured so that the "
":term:`User` does not call me because she does not find the icon on her "
"desktop!)."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'on attribue un paquet logiciel à une machine, on lui affecte le "
"nom canonique du logiciel sans son numéro de version (ex: je veux que "
":program:`Freemind` soit installé sur cette machine dans sa dernière "
"version et que :program:`Freemind` soit configuré pour que "
"l':term:`Utilisateur` ne m'appelle pas car il ne trouve pas l'icône sur "
"son bureau!)."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:289
msgid ""
"For each dependency, the WAPT agent will take care of automatically "
"installing the latest available package version. So if several versions "
"of :program:`Freemind` are available on the repository, the WAPT agent "
"will always get the latest version, unless I have pinned the version for "
"reason of compatibility with other sets of tools."
msgstr ""
"Pour chaque paquet en dépendance, l'agent WAPT local s'occupera d'aller "
"chercher automatiquement la dernière version du paquet. Donc si plusieurs"
" versions de :program:`Freemind` sont disponibles sur le dépôt, l'agent "
"WAPT ira toujours chercher la dernière version, à moins que vous ayez "
"épinglé la version pour cause de compatibilité avec d'autres outils."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:295
msgid ""
"Afterwards, when the agent contacts the repository to check for new "
"updates, it will compare the package versions on the repository with its "
"own local list of packages already installed on the machine."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, lorsque l'agent contacte le dépôt pour vérifier s'il y a de "
"nouvelles mises à jour, il compare les versions des paquets du dépôt avec"
" sa propre liste locale de paquets déjà installés sur la machine."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:299
msgid ""
"If an update of an installed package is available, the client will switch"
" the status of the package to **NEED UPGRADE**. It will then install the "
"software updates during the next :command:`upgrade`."
msgstr ""
"Si une mise à jour d'un paquet déjà installé est disponible, le client "
"basculera le statut du paquet en **NEED UPGRADE**. Il installera ainsi "
"les mises à jour au prochain :command:`upgrade`."

