#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:321
msgid "Private key/ public certificate"
msgstr "Principe de clé privée / clé publique"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:323
msgid ""
"To work properly, WAPT requires a private key/ public key pair (self-"
"signed, issued by an internal :term:`Certificate Authority` or "
"commercially issued)."
msgstr ""
"L'usage de WAPT nécessite un couple clé privée / certificat public (auto-"
"signé, issu d'une :term:`Autorité de Certification` interne, ou "
"commercial)."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:326
msgid ""
"The **private key** will be used to **sign** WAPT packages whereas the "
"**public key** will be distributed with every WAPT client so that WAPT "
"agents may validate the files that were signed with the private key."
msgstr ""
"La **clé privée** servira à **signer** les paquets WAPT et un "
"**certificat public** associé (CA associé ou certificat auto-signé) sera "
"distribué sur chaque client WAPT pour qu'il puisse valider les fichiers "
"signés avec la clé privée."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:330
msgid ""
"The different public keys will be stored in the WAPT subdirectory "
":file:`ssl`. That folder can contain several public keys."
msgstr ""
"Les différents certificats publics seront stockés dans un dossier "
":file:`ssl` de l'agent WAPT, ce dossier peut contenir plusieurs "
"certificats publics."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:334
msgid "Package verification"
msgstr "Vérification des paquets"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:336
msgid ""
"When a WAPT package is downloaded, the WAPT agent (:program:`waptagent`) "
"will check the integrity of the package, and then check that the package "
"has been properly **signed**."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'un paquet WAPT est téléchargé, l'agent WAPT (:program:`waptagent`)"
" vérifie l'integrité des fichiers, puis vérifie que le paquet a été "
"correctement **signé**."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:340
msgid ""
"If the WAPT package signature does not match any of the public keys "
"located in :file:`C:\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\wapt\\\\ssl`, the WAPT "
"agent will refuse to install the package."
msgstr ""
"Si la signature du paquet WAPT ne correspond à aucune des clés publiques "
"situées dans :file:`C:\\\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\\\wapt\\\\\\\\ssl`, "
"l'agent WAPT refusera d'installer le paquet."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:344
msgid ""
"For more information, please refer to the documentation on :ref:`how the "
"installation process integrity of a WAPT package is insured "
"<WAPT_package_installation_process_integrity>`."
msgstr ""
"Pour en savoir plus rendez-vous dans la section de documentation pour "
":ref:`protéger l'intégrité du processus d'installation des paquets WAPT "
"<WAPT_package_installation_process_integrity>`."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:349
msgid "The private certificate is important"
msgstr "Importance de la clé privée"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:353
msgid ""
"The private key must **NOT** be stored on the WAPT Server, nor on any "
"public or shared storage that could be accessed by non-authorized "
"personnel. Indeed, WAPT security is based on keeping the private key "
"**private**."
msgstr ""
"La clé privée ne doit pas être stockée sur le serveur WAPT, ni sur aucune"
" machine potentiellement accessible à une entité non-autorisée car toute "
"la sécurité de WAPT repose sur la confidentialité des jeux de clés "
"privées."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:357
msgid ""
"The private key must be stored in a safe place, because **she who has "
"your key controls your network**!"
msgstr ""
"Elle doit être stockée en lieu sûr car **celui qui contrôle votre clé "
"contrôle votre parc** !"

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:360
msgid ""
"Finally, to ensure maximum security, the private key can be secured in a "
"smartcard or a cryptographic token that WAPT :term:`Administrators` or "
":term:`Package Deployer` will carry physically on them, using the "
"smartcard or the token only when needed to sign a WAPT package."
msgstr ""
"Enfin, pour un maximum de sécurité, la clé privée pourra être une "
"smartcard ou un jeton cryptographique que les :term:`Administrateurs` et "
":term:`Déployeurs de Paquets` transporteront physiquement sur eux, "
"utilisant leur smartcard ou leur jeton cryptographique ponctuellement "
"pour signer un paquet WAPT."

#: /home/agauvrit/projects/doc-wapt/source/wapt-concept/index.rst:367
msgid ""
"From WAPT 1.5 onward, the private key is protected with a password by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Depuis la version 1.5 de WAPT, la clé privée est protégée par un mot de "
"passe."

